type   ) 

Value:

do { \
  if(!pointer) { \
    TMRM_ASSERT_REPORT("object pointer of type " #type " is NULL.") \
    TMRM_ASSERT_DIE \
    return; \
  } \
} while(0)

type,

    TMRM_ASSERT_DIE \
    return ret; \
  } \
} while(0)
